sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant U as User (authenticator)
    participant P as auth-api (:7011)
    participant R as Redis
    participant C as customer-api
    participant D as DynamoDB (banned)

    Note over U,D: Register (requires authenticated context)
    U->>P: POST /v1/passkeys/register/begin
    P->>R: store challenge, 5-min single-use
    P-->>U: PublicKeyCredentialCreationOptions
    U->>P: POST /v1/passkeys/register/complete (attestation)
    P->>R: consume challenge
    P->>P: verify attestation (UV=required, attestation=none)
    P->>C: store credential public key
    P-->>U: 201

    Note over U,D: Login (assertion)
    U->>P: POST /v1/passkeys/login/begin
    P->>R: store challenge, 5-min single-use
    P-->>U: PublicKeyCredentialRequestOptions
    U->>P: POST /v1/passkeys/login/complete (signed assertion)
    P->>R: consume challenge
    P->>C: fetch credential public key
    P->>P: verify assertion + sign-count
    P->>D: banned-customer gate
    P-->>U: access + refresh token
